{"tid":1210393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[上車先] 居屋申請截止　截至下午5時收到近30萬份申請","createTime":"2019-06-12T13:40:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T14:50:09.000Z","uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d021c77a19406405c1d03d25494c9246c1336537","tid":1210393,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:40:39.000Z","msg":"新一期居屋晚上7時截止申請，市民把握最後機會到樂富房委會客務中心遞交申請表。截至下午5時，累計收到約共100000份居屋或白居二申請表。在網上申請方面，房委會累計收到約196000份居屋和97000份白居二申請。<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1462454_2_L_20190612210931.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1462454_2_L_20190612210931.jpg&h=43e2668d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n客務中心累計派出約共205000份申請表，當中約58000份是居屋綠表和147000份是居屋或白居二的白表。<br />\n<br />\n有前往客務中心交表的老師馬小姐表示，私樓難以負擔，所以選擇申請居屋。又說因為6月正值學期尾，工作繁忙，又要花時間選定單位，所以在即將截止申請時交表。<br />\n<br />\n今期出售6個新建居屋發展項目包括何文田冠德苑、長沙灣凱德苑、荃灣尚文苑、將軍澳雍明苑、馬鞍山錦暉苑及沙田旭禾苑合共4871個單位，售價由最平156萬至529萬元。預計8月攪珠，11月揀樓。"},{"pid":"0ca5ca95d5ffc2830144cbc908fef8819835a951","tid":1210393,"uid":256014,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T14:50:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"> 　　今天</span><span style=\"color: red;\">CHECK</span><span style=\"color: green;\">自己</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">支票戶口</span>扣了＄４１０，<span style=\"color: green;\">我</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">告知</span><span style=\"color: green;\">阿媽，阿媽</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">話</span><span style=\"color: green;\">阿爸</span><span style=\"color: red;\">俾番</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">＄４１０</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">給</span><span style=\"color: green;\">我，我</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">話</span>唔要，<span style=\"color: green;\">我自己</span><span style=\"color: red;\">有錢，俾番</span><span style=\"color: green;\">阿爸，我</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">現在</span><span style=\"color: red;\">希望</span><span style=\"color: green;\">自己</span>抽唔到<span style=\"color: brown;\">（因為</span><span style=\"color: red;\">抽到，</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">之後</span>無錢去採熊），<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">　　事緣</span><span style=\"color: green;\">爸爸</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">較早前</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">於</span><span style=\"color: green;\">樂富</span><span style=\"color: violet;\">拿了</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">「白居二</span> <span style=\"color: limegreen;\">　２０１９」</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">申請表</span><span style=\"color: violet;\">回家，</span><span style=\"color: green;\">我自己</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">第一次</span><span style=\"color: red;\">填表</span><span style=\"color: red;\">申請</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">「白居二</span> <span style=\"color: limegreen;\">　２０１９」</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">及</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">「居屋</span> <span style=\"color: limegreen;\">　２０１９」（一人</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">申請表，</span>唔知填得啱唔啱，<span style=\"color: brown;\">當好似</span><span style=\"color: violet;\">返工填</span><span style=\"color: red;\">假紙【備註】），</span><span style=\"color: green;\">我</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">是</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">郵寄</span><span style=\"color: red;\">申請</span><span style=\"color: green;\">（我</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">當時</span><span style=\"color: violet;\">放</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">信件</span><span style=\"color: violet;\">入</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">郵筒</span><span style=\"color: red;\">希望</span><span style=\"color: green;\">自己</span>填表填錯<span style=\"color: orange;\">或</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">郵件</span>送不到目的地），怎料<span style=\"color: red;\">過了數，<br />\n<br />\n　　【備註】：</span><span style=\"color: green;\">我自己</span>英文有限公司，<span style=\"color: green;\">我</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">現職</span><span style=\"color: green;\">公司</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">請假紙</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">是</span><span style=\"color: green;\">英文，</span>唔識填就無得放。</strong></span>"}]}